TASK: 
"You have a payment order form paper example.
Need to create REST endpoint which proceeds payment details and sends email about received payment"

WHAT IT DOES:
Receives REST API POST request with payment order details as a JSON, makes basic payment information checks 
and sends an e-mail containing received payment information to a specified e-mail address

Uses gmail service -> gmail account required

Enter e-mail and app password in application.properties before launch

Before running unit tests:
Enter target e-mail address into comment specified lines
